originalSql:
SELECT 
    t.title AS movie_title,
    a.name AS actor_name,
    r.role AS actor_role,
    c.name AS company_name,
    m.info AS movie_info
FROM 
    title t
JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
JOIN 
    company_name c ON mc.company_id = c.id
JOIN 
    complete_cast cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id
JOIN 
    cast_info ci ON cc.subject_id = ci.person_id
JOIN 
    aka_name a ON ci.person_id = a.person_id
JOIN 
    role_type r ON ci.role_id = r.id
LEFT JOIN 
    movie_info m ON t.id = m.movie_id
WHERE 
    t.production_year >= 2000
ORDER BY 
    t.production_year DESC, 
    a.name

SELECT COALESCE("title"."title", "title"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "aka_name"."name" AS "ACTOR_NAME", "s1"."role" AS "ACTOR_ROLE", "company_name"."name" AS "COMPANY_NAME", "movie_info"."info" AS "MOVIE_INFO", "title"."production_year"
FROM "title"
INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"
INNER JOIN "complete_cast" ON "title"."id" = "complete_cast"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "complete_cast"."subject_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "cast_info"."role_id" = "s1"."id"
LEFT JOIN "movie_info" ON "title"."id" = "movie_info"."movie_id"
WHERE "title"."production_year" >= 2000
ORDER BY "title"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "aka_name"."name"

SELECT COALESCE("id", "id") AS "id", "movie_id", "info_type_id", "info", "note"
FROM "movie_info"

SELECT COALESCE("title"."title", "title"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "aka_name"."name" AS "ACTOR_NAME", "role_type"."role" AS "ACTOR_ROLE", "company_name"."name" AS "COMPANY_NAME", "s1"."info" AS "MOVIE_INFO", "title"."production_year"
FROM "title"
INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"
INNER JOIN "complete_cast" ON "title"."id" = "complete_cast"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "complete_cast"."subject_id" = "cast_info"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "role_type" ON "cast_info"."role_id" = "role_type"."id"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "title"."id" = "s1"."movie_id"
WHERE "title"."production_year" >= 2000
ORDER BY "title"."production_year" DESC NULLS FIRST, "aka_name"."name"
